        <a href="http://arstechnica.com/science/2022/03/exploring-the-counterintuitive-mysteries-of-black-holes-with-paul-sutter/?comments=1&post=40789188#comment-40789188" title="2022-03-30T14:12:34+00:00" class="timeago datetime" rel="nofollow">Wed Mar 30, 2022 9:12 am</a>
        
